{
  "stem": "7506.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES] That happened where my grandparents lived, in the area where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But where we lived at that time, we didn't have such an area for a while.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't really and truly recall that my mother sat my sister and I down and said, from tomorrow, we all have to wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember her saying that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She may well have done that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All I remember is that they were on my jacket, or my coat, a star like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got the star-- [PAUSES] I would say, approximately a year after the occupation of Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably around about 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would have been nine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I do not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I do not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only-- I remember one particular occasion when one friend of mine-- obviously, we were all about the same age-- [PAUSES] said to me-- and although it's very young-- I remember him saying in Dutch-- and I will tell you the Dutch.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will translate it for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING DUTCH], meaning, I knew you were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- that sort of [PAUSES] made me kind of inwardly jump.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But apart from that, no, I don't remember anybody pointing their finger, that I noticed, at me at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I-- I felt no different than before, except that I was somewhat more aware of being different.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even more intensified [PAUSES] from the time I wore the star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, the intensity got much worse as the time progressed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, I was not going to the Jewish school anymore, because the Jewish school was in the old part of Amsterdam, where we had lived before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was afraid to take me there because of the razzias.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
